   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "ce41dc04-94a7-464b-9fb0-41261f8108a7",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data = pd.read_csv(r'C:\\Users\\BALAJI R\\Downloads\\headbrain.csv')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "7c2cc2ea-72a2-4c31-93aa-87653278f16a",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "X = data['Head Size(cm^3)'].values\n",
    "y = data['Brain Weight(grams)'].values"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "f228397c-a523-4d1e-a624-67219105e6df",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "mean_x = np.mean(X)\n",
    "mean_y = np.mean(y)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "b8b062b0-5f39-456c-8069-8319d4f3884d",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "m = np.sum((X - mean_x) * (y - mean_y)) / np.sum((X - mean_x) ** 2)\n",
    "b = mean_y - m * mean_x"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "id": "7257fc6c-8447-4c72-a6d3-461e93b635dc",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "predicted_y = m * X + b"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "id": "15a54086-a547-4956-bed9-c759e066d5d6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "plt.scatter(X, y, color=\"blue\", label=\"Data Points\")\n",
    "plt.plot(X, predicted_y, color=\"red\", label=\"Regression Line\")\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Head Size (cm^3)')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Brain Weight (grams)')\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 15,
   "id": "18dba6f5-34b4-4ac1-b057-39d0545c19e5",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "TSS = np.sum((y - mean_y) ** 2)\n",
    "RSS = np.sum((y - predicted_y) ** 2)  \n",
    "R_squared = 1 - (RSS / TSS)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 17,
   "id": "b5a5e1b4-a730-4cf7-9065-f507b732a0f9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Slope (m): 0.2634293394893993\n",
      "Intercept (b): 325.5734210494428\n",
      "R-squared value: 0.639311719957\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "print(f\"Slope (m): {m}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Intercept (b): {b}\")\n",
    "print(f\"R-squared value: {R_squared}\")"
   ]
  },
